code a personal website and blog using the next.js JavaScript framework and the Chakra-UI css framework. We override and create a custom theme, add a dark mode, create and modify _app.js and _document.js, and set up the index.js page for the rest of the videos. Be sure to watch part 2 where we finish off the remainder of this video. link:https://youtu.be/lhOvI9s5gQY | https://youtu.be/G6_qqMrfTQg  code :https://github.com/bjcarlson42/personal-website-nextjs-chakra